{"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/vigramsdk\/useperipheralconfiguration"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"primaryContentSections":[{"content":[{"text":"","anchor":"","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"If you need to disable some GNSS messages, change the message rate, or change the minimum elevation used in navigation parameters, create a ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.vigramsdk\/documentation\/VigramSDK\/PeripheralConfiguration"},{"text":" and pass it to the peripheral initializer.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Example:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["let peripheralConfiguration =","    PeripheralConfiguration(rateOfChangeMessages: .hertz1,","                            glonassActivate: false)"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Then pass the configuration to the peripheral initializer:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["\/\/ If use support logger, configure it once with Vigram.Logger(...)","\/\/ and then create the peripheral normally","let sdkPeripheral =","    Vigram.peripheral(cbPeripheral,","                      configuration: peripheralConfiguration)","","\/\/ Without a custom configuration","let defaultPeripheral = Vigram.peripheral(cbPeripheral)"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Note: If this parameter is not passed to the initializer, all parameters will use their default values.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["\/\/ Message rate is set to 7 hertz","rateOfChangeMessages: RateValue = .hertz7","","\/\/ Minimum elevation used in navigation is set to 10 degrees","elevationValue: ElevationValue = .ang10,","","\/\/ All satellite constellations are active","glonassActivate = true","beidouActivate = true","galileoActivate = true","qzssActivate = true","sbassActivate = true","","\/\/ NAV-DOP and NAV-PVT messages are active","navDOPActivate 